OL,3,CPlans to punish criminals who avoid
OL,4,Csentencing 'step in right direction'
OL,6,FNew powers for judges to punish
OL,7,Fcriminals who refuse to attend their
OL,8,Fsentencing hearings sends a "clear
OL,9,Fmessage" that offenders cannot "opt
OL,10,Fout" of justice, victims' families
OL,11,Fhave said.
OL,13,FPlans for tougher sanctions in England
OL,14,Fand Wales, including more jail time or
OL,15,Floss of privileges in prison, are
OL,16,Famong the measures in the Government's
OL,17,FVictims and Courts Bill to be
OL,18,Fintroduced to Parliament on Wednesday.
