OL,3,CPlans to punish criminals who avoid
OL,4,Csentencing 'step in right direction'
OL,6,FThe move comes after a series of high
OL,7,Fprofile offenders refusing to face
OL,8,Fvictims' families sparked a public
OL,9,Foutcry, and calls by campaigners for a
OL,10,Fchange in the law.
OL,12,FFamilies of murdered primary school
OL,13,Fteacher Sabina Nessa, law graduate
OL,14,FZara Aleena and mother-of-three Jan
OL,15,FMustafa are among those to have
OL,16,Fcampaigned for the change after their
OL,17,Floved ones' killers were absent from
OL,18,Fsentencing hearings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
