OL,3,CPlans to punish criminals who avoid
OL,4,Csentencing 'step in right direction'
OL,6,FReacting to the "long-awaited"
OL,7,Fproposals, Ms Nessa's sister Jebina
OL,8,FIslam, Ms Aleena's aunt Farah Naz and
OL,9,FMs Mustafa's cousin Ayse Hussein,
OL,10,Fsaid: "This move holds offenders to
OL,11,Faccount.
OL,13,F"It sends a clear and necessary
OL,14,Fmessage: the justice system is not
OL,15,Fsomething you should be able to opt
OL,16,Fout of.
