OL,3,CPlans to punish criminals who avoid
OL,4,Csentencing 'step in right direction'
OL,6,F"It is not about punishment through
OL,7,Fforce ` but about ensuring that
OL,8,Fperpetrators cannot remove themselves
OL,9,Ffrom the consequences of their
OL,10,Factions."
OL,12,FTheir joint statement said the
OL,13,Flegislation was a "step in the right
OL,14,Fdirection" alongside wider campaigns,
OL,15,Fand that the proposed punishments
OL,16,Findicated "this change is being taken
OL,17,Fseriously".
OL,19,FThey added: "This change supports
OL,20,Fvictims and society alike. It shows
OL,21,Fjustice being done.
