OL,6,FThomas Cashman, the gunman who killed
OL,7,FOlivia as he chased a drug dealer who
OL,8,Fhad tried to run into her home in
OL,9,FKnotty Ash, Liverpool, did not appear
OL,10,Fin court to hear his life sentence in
OL,11,FApril 2023.
OL,13,FMs Korbel's MP, Anneliese Midgley,
OL,14,Fsaid of the legislation: "This law is
OL,15,Fdown in no small part to my
OL,16,Fconstituent Cheryl Korbel. I am so
OL,17,Fproud of her.
