OL,3,CPlans to punish criminals who avoid
OL,4,Csentencing 'step in right direction'
OL,6,F"Sentencing is not just a legal
OL,7,Fformality; it is the culmination of
OL,8,Fjustice. That's why it's so important
OL,9,Fthat justice is not only done, but
OL,10,Fseen to be done.
OL,12,F"Olivia's Law will make sure it is."
OL,14,FUnder the new legislation, judges will
OL,15,Fbe given the power to sentence
OL,16,Foffenders for up to two more years in
OL,17,Fprison for avoiding justice.
