OL,3,CPlans to punish criminals who avoid
OL,4,Csentencing 'step in right direction'
OL,6,FEarlier this year, triple crossbow and
OL,7,Fknife killer Kyle Clifford refused to
OL,8,Fattend his sentencing where he
OL,9,Freceived a whole life order in March,
OL,10,Fwhile Southport child-murderer Axel
OL,11,FRudakubana avoided facing victims'
OL,12,Ffamilies as he was removed from his
OL,13,Fhearing for repeatedly shouting in
OL,14,FJanuary.
OL,16,FThe measure could apply to any case in
OL,17,Fthe crown court, and include those
OL,18,Fsuch as Rudakubana who attended
OL,19,Fproceedings but was removed from the
OL,20,Fcourtroom for disruptive behaviour.
