OL,6,FJustice minister Alex Davies-Jones
OL,7,Fsaid: "I would like to thank the
OL,8,Fremarkable families of Olivia Pratt-
OL,9,FKorbel, Jan Mustafa, Sabina Nessa and
OL,10,FZara Aleena and countless others who
OL,11,Fhave campaigned tirelessly for
OL,12,Foffenders to have to face the reality
OL,13,Fof their crimes by attending their
OL,14,Fsentencing.
OL,16,F"Justice isn't optional ` we'll make
OL,17,Fsure criminals face their victims."
