OL,6,FThe Bill also plans to restrict
OL,7,Fparental responsibility from child sex
OL,8,Foffenders who committed serious crimes
OL,9,Fagainst their own child to boost
OL,10,Fprotection for victims.
OL,12,FThe move will stop them being able to
OL,13,Fask for updates on their child's
OL,14,Fschooling or trying to interfere in
OL,15,Ftheir life.
