OL,6,FVictims' Commissioner for England and
OL,7,FWales, Baroness Newlove, said: "These
OL,8,Fimportant and welcome reforms give the
OL,9,FVictims' Commissioner the statutory
OL,10,Fpowers needed to deliver on the role's
OL,11,Fpromise: championing victims' rights,
OL,12,Fscrutinising compliance with the
OL,13,FVictims' Code, holding agencies to
OL,14,Faccount, and spotlighting the true
OL,15,Fvictim experience to drive meaningful
OL,16,Fchange.
