OL,6,FSam Whyte, of the NSPCC, said: "These
OL,7,Fmeasures must be part of broader
OL,8,Fefforts to create a truly accountable
OL,9,Fcriminal justice system.
OL,11,F"That must include Government using
OL,12,Fthe upcoming Comprehensive Spending
OL,13,FReview to commit the considerable
OL,14,Finvestment needed in specific support
OL,15,Ffor victims and survivors of child
OL,16,Fsexual abuse, so that every child can
OL,17,Faccess the support they need, where
OL,18,Fand when they need it."
